title: Air Chief calls on Prime Minister
content:
ISLAMABAD, Mar 11 (APP): Chief of the Air Staff Air Chief Marshal Zaheer Ahmad Babar Sidhu on Monday called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here.
The Air Chief congratulated Prime Minister Shehbaz on assuming the office, a PM Office press release said.
In the meeting, they discussed the professional matters of the Pakistan Air Force.
